free-exercise-db
================

Source:   https://github.com/yuhonas/free-exercise-db
Snapshot: dist/exercises.json (873 records), retrieved 2026-06-29.
License:  The Unlicense (public domain) — https://unlicense.org/

This is free and unencumbered data released into the public domain.
Anyone is free to copy, modify, publish, use, compile, sell, or distribute
it, for any purpose, commercial or non-commercial, and by any means.

Exercise illustration imagery referenced via imageURL is hosted from the same
repository under the same public-domain dedication:
  https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yuhonas/free-exercise-db/main/exercises/<path>

DailyFitness ingests this snapshot via scripts/import-exercises.py and normalizes
it into Resources/Exercises/exercises.json. Curated yoga/mobility/flexibility
records (scripts/data/curated_exercises.json) plus a deterministic combinatorial
strength expansion supplement this dataset to reach the >=2,000-exercise library.
